tutorial: https://www.reddit.com/r/archlinux/comments/exr82b/tried_55_from_testing_and_wifi_rtl8822be_stopped/

sudo touch /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf

Add to blacklist.conf following lines:
lacklist btrtl
blacklist btusb
blacklist r8822be
blacklist rtw88
blacklist rtwpci



#-----------------------------------------------------------#

do not install xorg and xorg-server
rfkill list all
